00922 void testBinaryDataOnly()
00923 {
00924     MSData tiny;
00925     examples::initializeTiny(tiny);
00926 
00927     MSData tinier;
00928     SpectrumListSimplePtr sl(new SpectrumListSimple);
00929     tinier.run.spectrumListPtr = sl; 
00930 
00931     for (unsigned int i=0; i<tiny.run.spectrumListPtr->size(); i++)
00932     {
00933         SpectrumPtr from = tiny.run.spectrumListPtr->spectrum(i, true);
00934         sl->spectra.push_back(SpectrumPtr(new Spectrum));
00935         SpectrumPtr& to = sl->spectra.back();   
00936 
00937         for (vector<BinaryDataArrayPtr>::const_iterator it=from->binaryDataArrayPtrs.begin();
00938              it!=from->binaryDataArrayPtrs.end(); ++it)
00939         {
00940             // copy BinaryDataArray::data from tiny to tinier
00941             to->binaryDataArrayPtrs.push_back(BinaryDataArrayPtr(new BinaryDataArray));
00942             to->binaryDataArrayPtrs.back()->data = (*it)->data;
00943         }
00944 
00945         // copy "important" scan metadata
00946 
00947         to->index = from->index;
00948         to->nativeID = from->nativeID;
00949         to->defaultArrayLength = from->defaultArrayLength;
00950 
00951         to->spectrumDescription.precursors.resize(from->spectrumDescription.precursors.size());
00952         for (size_t precursorIndex=0; precursorIndex<from->spectrumDescription.precursors.size(); ++precursorIndex)
00953         {
00954             Precursor& precursorTo = to->spectrumDescription.precursors[precursorIndex];
00955             Precursor& precursorFrom = from->spectrumDescription.precursors[precursorIndex];
00956             precursorTo.ionSelection = precursorFrom.ionSelection;
00957         }
00958     }
00959 
00960     if (os_)
00961     {
00962         *os_ << "tinier::";
00963         TextWriter(*os_,0)(tinier);
00964     }
00965 
00966     Diff<MSData> diff_full(tiny, tinier);
00967     unit_assert(diff_full);
00968 
00969     DiffConfig config;
00970     config.ignoreMetadata = true;
00971 
00972     Diff<MSData> diff_data(tiny, tinier, config);
00973     if (os_ && diff_data) *os_ << diff_data << endl;
00974     unit_assert(!diff_data);
00975 }
